<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  
  
  <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/bootstrap-icons/1.10.0/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    /* Additional custom styles (if needed) */
    .accordion-button {
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .accordion-body {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }
    .text-purple {
      color: purple;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container py-5">
    <h1 class="display-4 text-center text-primary mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
    <p class="text-center text-muted mb-5">
      Discover everything you need to know about NoteNestPro. We've curated answers to the most common queries to make your experience seamless!
    </p>
   
    <div class="accordion accordion-flush shadow-lg rounded" id="faqAccordion">
      <!-- FAQ 1 -->
      <div class="accordion-item border-bottom">
        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faq1">
          <button class="accordion-button bg-light text-dark fw-bold" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse1" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapse1">
            <i class="bi bi-question-circle me-2 text-primary"></i>
            What is NoteNestPro?
          </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapse1" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" aria-labelledby="faq1" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
          <div class="accordion-body bg-white text-secondary">
            NoteNestPro is a free app that allows you to create, update, and manage your notes effortlessly, ensuring your important data is always at hand.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ 2 -->
      <div class="accordion-item border-bottom">
        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faq2">
          <button class="accordion-button bg-light collapsed text-dark fw-bold" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse2" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse2">
            <i class="bi bi-pencil-square me-2 text-primary"></i>
            How can I create a new note?
          </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapse2" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq2" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
          <div class="accordion-body bg-white text-secondary">
            You can create a new note by clicking on the "New Note" button in the dashboard. It's intuitive and quick!
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ 3 -->
      <div class="accordion-item border-bottom">
        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faq3">
          <button class="accordion-button bg-light collapsed text-dark fw-bold" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse3" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse3">
            <i class="bi bi-lock-fill me-2 text-primary"></i>
            Is my data secure?
          </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapse3" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq3" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
          <div class="accordion-body bg-white text-secondary">
            Yes, all your data is securely stored and encrypted for your privacy. We prioritize your data's safety.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ 4 -->
      <div class="accordion-item border-bottom">
        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faq4">
          <button class="accordion-button bg-light collapsed text-dark fw-bold" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse4" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse4">
            <i class="bi bi-cloud-arrow-down-fill me-2 text-primary"></i>
            Can I access my notes on multiple devices?
          </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapse4" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq4" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
          <div class="accordion-body bg-white text-secondary">
            Absolutely! Your notes are synced across devices in real time, so you can access them from anywhere.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ 5 -->
      <div class="accordion-item border-bottom">
        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faq5">
          <button class="accordion-button bg-light collapsed text-dark fw-bold" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse5" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse5">
            <i class="bi bi-person-gear me-2 text-primary"></i>
            Can I customize my notes?
          </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapse5" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq5" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
          <div class="accordion-body bg-white text-secondary">
            Yes, you can add tags, categories, and even customize note formatting to suit your workflow.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>